---
title: Sticky Chutney Chicken Strips  with Roasted Veggies & Smokey Aioli
description: Here’s a hearty chicken bowl that draws inspiration from countless cuisines and brings it straight to your table. Herby
chicken strips, coated in a sweet chutney meets roast veggie toss, and there’s a dollop of hollandaise to finish it off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
